n characters. They can be selected by any character who meets their prerequisites.</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.Lwz3gOMtKNe0wQeV]{Unicorn: Animal Companion}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.pmG6pQqsd8WkQuwJ]{Unicorn: Seasoned Rider}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.58jg2qN8dEyqFYyK]{Unicorn: Trade Expert}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.mo4xTTJyurey7DqD]{Unicorn: Unwavering Heart}</p><h1><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Table 5–4: Animal Companion Options</span></h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SvtRx7J.png\" />","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":1100000,"name":"Imperial Family Feats","type":"text","_id":"yRQlfmSF0kAo5h5c","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>AiR p.234</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">The following feats are suggested options for building iconic Imperial characters. They can be selected by any character who meets their prerequisites.</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.FnmR5FmR53MxqOFX]{Imperial: Celestial Authority}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Imperial Family background or Charisma 15 or higher</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":1200000,"name":"Minor Clan Feats","type":"text","_id":"xtCvuZAjWqjQrDlW","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>AiR p.234</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">The following feats are suggested options for building iconic Minor Clan characters. They can be selected by any character who meets their prerequisites.</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.evvckFGpdu0ewV43]{Minor: Dreamscape Journey}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Moth Clan background or proficiency in Religion</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.VAxHLwCHLB9pycyR]{Minor: Exorcist’s Sight}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Falcon Clan background or proficiency in Arcana</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.asW60I3zD9tQadzx]{Minor: Favor of Lady Sun}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong>rerequisite</strong>: Centipede Clan background or proficiency in Religion, must be able to perform invocations</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.0v8obLOLXHdtWI5m]{Minor: Hearty Boast}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Mantis Clan background or proficiency in Performanc</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.qeNMzEJlaEn6zoIr]{Minor: Innocuous Presence}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Deer Clan background or proficiency in Stealth</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.jpNZo8kETYSrAxIj]{Minor: Killing Grip}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Badger Clan background or proficiency in Athletics</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.G66tRBNswUS9bUAC]{Minor: “Legitimate Business Connections”}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Tortoise Clan background or proficiency in Sleight of Hand</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.X5s6W0BHxOodDRcq]{Minor: Phantom Thief}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Cat Clan background or proficiency in sleight of hand</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.V48WMmcTdsJvasnd]{Minor: Sling Specialist}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Sparrow Clan background or proficiency in Survival</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.2Zav6O0efSHBOWOS]{Minor: Spiritual Evasion}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Hare Clan background or proficiency in Religion</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.97IebJwgThmJqZm0]{Minor: Sting of Agony}</p><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Wasp Clan background or proficiency in Perception</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":1300000,"name":"Regional Background Feats","type":"text","_id":"MWz3HyORvhNf2x9i","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>AiR p.237</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">The following feats are suggested options for building iconic characters from various regional backgrounds. They can be selected by any character who meets their prerequisites.</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.BNuFaPjywrGwWPeh]{Regional: Artisan’s Ingenuity}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Non-samurai background or Charisma 15 or higher</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.uc93gcUBn7683VWc]{Regional: Brawler’s Edge}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Non-samurai background or Strength 15 or higher</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.myIE1qtHAjPiKOHq]{Regional: Laborer’s Endurance}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Non-samurai background or Constitution 15 or higher</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.YPynGMNDmVXOH1oC]{Regional: Merchant’s Streetwise}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Non-samurai background or Dexterity 15 or higher</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.H75CYnYGuaK5a2tA]{Regional: Survivalist’s Eye}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Non-samurai background or Wisdom 15 or higher</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.msVurUo9hA8pQljn]{Regional: Translator’s Knowledge}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Non-samurai background or Intelligence 15 or higher</span></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":1400000,"name":"Species Feats","type":"text","_id":"2D8Jy59lwEsenK7M","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>AiR p.238</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">The following feats enhance the unique physiological abilities of non-human characters. They can be selected by any character who meets their prerequisites.</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.wX91fgdOyoNTZSAz]{Species: Constriction}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Naga species</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.yb34QnHaglj4bOII]{Species: Enhanced Demonic Transformation}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Mazoku species</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.sTx7I6ZEkQD5PjSw]{Species: Haunting Phenomena}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Specter species</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.pmQzv7ri38Z9mF2c]{Species: Nimble Glider}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Tengu species</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.UFlWJvX2hmMHJ6w6]{Species: Persistence}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Human species</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.9BOwlmhOTrKzznOM]{Species: Scamper}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisite</strong>: Nezumi species</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.air-compendium.feats.B2qQMmIkJY22NbQw]{Species: Skilled Shapeshifter}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Prerequisites</strong>: Animal yōkai species</span></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"FHMpmEo8beZuKfc9":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.tmBuMRAZ8nRxnucU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1678142264002,"modifiedTime":1680116455577,"lastModifiedBy":"FHMpmEo8beZuKfc9"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"mdgyynVHONQlncyF"}
{"name":"Book 0: Chapter 0: Introduction","pages":[{"sort":100000,"name":"Introduction","type":"text","_id":"tO6O7GKnREvPHNEa","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>AiR p.4</p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">Welcome to the Emerald Empire, or Rokugan. This is a land of chivalry, romance, and heroism. <strong>Adventures in Rokugan</strong> brings the longstanding setting of The Legend of the Five Rings to the world’s most famous roleplaying game.</span></p><p></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":0,"name":"Cover Art","type":"image","_id":"YOA7ZSdi4Xqann6b","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{"caption":""},"text":{"format":1},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":"https://i.imgur.com/oY9m5vQ.png","system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":-100000,"name":"Cover","type":"image","_id":"6vNdrQsNSKiImOk7","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{"caption":""},"text":{"format":1},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":"https://i.imgur.com/bv76Jub.png","system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":50000,"name":"Credits","type":"text","_id":"Dmh4BVpFO6SmsEL6","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>AiR p.2</p><p><span class=\"fontstyle1\">MECHANICS DESIGN AND DEVELOPMENT<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">Max Brooke with Welden Bringhurst</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle1\">NARRATIVE DESIGN AND DEVELOPMENT<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">Lydia Suen</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle1\">PROOFREADING<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">Kate Cunningham and Tova Seltzer</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle1\">SENSITIVITY REVIEW<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\